text: maybe "tempo" instead of "spell voltron"?
i think of tempo as outpacing opponents in the playing of cards
like bouncing things to the top of their library
slowing down opponent cards, but different from stax
trading resources for a temporary advantage to close out the game quickly - is how I'd describe all the instants/sorceries in this list
but mostly I think "spell voltron" isn't in the vernacular
if we called it "Spelltron", would people know what we meant?
between that and spell voltron I'd prefer spell voltron
